  "text": "Myeloperoxidase (MPO) activity represents an index of neutrophil and monocyte/macrophage activation [CITATION_1] . We assayed MPO activity in serum of lung cancer patients using a commercial kit (BioVision, CA, USA), according to the manufacturer's recommended protocol.",
